  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/e65eef69befbaac35940352167ce8cdc.avif?t=1770272927\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras_big/e65eef69befbaac35940352167ce8cdc.avif?t=1770272927 width=800 height=1593 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ketz: Galactic Overlords</strong> is a sci-fi fantasy-themed roguelite horde survival game with RPG elements. Choose your character, collect various gear, and create game-breaking builds using powerful skills from the Galactic Leaders. Find out why the Galactic Leaders chose to help you.<strong> </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/22a7dc3493d4b557b6ca4d7ac01c01e9.webp?t=1770272927\" width=616 height=34 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                          Rare Gear Made Easy with Master Tinket!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/860b565388be52e29b5e48436af841a6.poster.avif?t=1770272927\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/860b565388be52e29b5e48436af841a6.webm?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/860b565388be52e29b5e48436af841a6.mp4?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use Master Tinket to upgrade your gear and reach rare items. Placing the same type of item will increase your chances of obtaining the desired equipment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                   Different Skill Combinations = Different Strategies </strong><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/416eb237c7f63c8c8fd11af1415eff56.poster.avif?t=1770272927\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/416eb237c7f63c8c8fd11af1415eff56.webm?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/416eb237c7f63c8c8fd11af1415eff56.mp4?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Choose from 9 Galactic Leaders who have allied with you against Ketzeror, discover the skill combinations that suit you best, and craft your battle strategy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                                      Hammathor: Lord of the Rats!</strong><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/ab25c02a0fc34034dfa027eb826f1088.poster.avif?t=1770272927\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/ab25c02a0fc34034dfa027eb826f1088.webm?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/ab25c02a0fc34034dfa027eb826f1088.mp4?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to face Hammathor, Lady Ketzeror’s first commander? The leader of the rats and the ultimate being of his kind, Hammathor crushes his enemies with cunning and brutality. Do you have what it takes to defeat him?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                 Knowledge is Power: Strike a Deal with Orin Vaal! </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/b0b0c5f101f28a96304d14699ede13cf.poster.avif?t=1770272927\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/b0b0c5f101f28a96304d14699ede13cf.webm?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/b0b0c5f101f28a96304d14699ede13cf.mp4?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Orin Vaal is passionate about research. Bring him books to support his studies, and in return, claim precious gemstones. Use these mystical stones to enhance your power and upgrade your gear!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                                         Unleash Your Full Potential!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/8c367fa623cb546c7e62a513bb2b13c2.poster.avif?t=1770272927\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/8c367fa623cb546c7e62a513bb2b13c2.webm?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/8c367fa623cb546c7e62a513bb2b13c2.mp4?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the maximum power of your chosen character, craft the best build with various abilities, and push your limits! Adapt your strategy, withstand relentless waves of enemies, and survive as long as you can!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                   Lord Synthrex: The Mighty Guardian of Ketzeror!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/847a1e59637f9526cf6379cc54299b46.poster.avif?t=1770272927\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/847a1e59637f9526cf6379cc54299b46.webm?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/847a1e59637f9526cf6379cc54299b46.mp4?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The end of the road is just the beginning… Lord Synthrex! The unyielding ally of Lady Ketzeror and the first great trial you must overcome to reach her!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you withstand his power, or will your galactic journey end here?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/22a7dc3493d4b557b6ca4d7ac01c01e9.webp?t=1770272927\" width=616 height=34 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ketz: Galactic Overlords</strong> is a sci-fi fantasy-themed roguelite horde survival game with RPG elements. Choose your character, collect various gear, and create game-breaking builds using powerful skills from the Galactic Leaders. Find out why the Galactic Leaders chose to help you.<strong> </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/22a7dc3493d4b557b6ca4d7ac01c01e9.webp?t=1770272927\" width=616 height=34 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                          Rare Gear Made Easy with Master Tinket!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/860b565388be52e29b5e48436af841a6.poster.avif?t=1770272927\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/860b565388be52e29b5e48436af841a6.webm?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/860b565388be52e29b5e48436af841a6.mp4?t=1770272927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use Master Tinket to upgrade your gear and reach rare items. Placing the same type of item will increase your chances of obtaining the desired equipment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                   Different Skill Combinations = Different Strategies </strong><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542140/extras/416eb237c7f63c8c8fd11af1415eff56.poster.avif?t=1770272927\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/